reviews.text: Guess this is a place for tea and dessert, and when it comes to hot dishes, no expectation.
Mini cake shop with mainly Japanese influenced macha desserts, drinks, and cakes.
Japanese chef is so interesting !!
各種日式料理，即叫即製，Good!
昨晚吃飯經過，店內只有兩位客人，晚上七時到，還有很還有少量的食物尚未售完，地方也10分寬敞，下一次可以試呢。
